# Docs Rule Router

For `docs/superpowers/**/*.md` or `docs/ai/**/*.md` work, read:

- `docs/ai/rules/spec-plan-workflow.md`

If the change affects architecture, also read:

- `docs/ai/rules/project-context.md`

If the change affects quality gates or generated command flows, also read:

- `docs/ai/rules/linting-and-quality.md`
